{"tid":2325401,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個魚拉突，咁既抽籤真係得啖笑","createTime":"2020-12-14T14:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T05:57:08.000Z","uid":70439,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a5b01fed67679578fa99c5e0db214c2c0f22c125","tid":2325401,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T14:12:57.000Z","msg":"講真咁同直接宣佈曼晉級有咩分別。<br />\n<br />\n令我地班魚拉突 totally no mood to 捱夜睇波 嗱,我又分析下 <br />\n<br />\n皇家蘇斯達,,如果係皇馬就有可觀性(順便可以報上次ga仇)(不過算啦,入到歐洲超級盃又會見到面) 我真係冇睇過依隊野..曼半力夠WIN,又雙勝<br />\n<br />\n加上我地4大尖刀 福仔,馬仔,綠木,連仔 加上關鍵王般奴.. 根本場場大炒,,,,<br />\n<br />\n出線就一定..係睇下破唔破到得失球.咁一面倒ga比賽,我冇興趣,大家16強見<br />\n<br />\nP.S.比d咁ga對手魚拉突..is侮辱..哈"},{"pid":"21ae8f9cc49bf134eddaa9c3cedffa2b81800089","tid":2325401,"uid":200083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T14:13:50.000Z","msg":"... ,,, ga ga .. ,,,"},{"pid":"3ff6f208b91ad6345243e3ce49ffcfc091aeeeac","tid":2325401,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T14:16:29.000Z","msg":"皇家蘇斯黃"},{"pid":"2969f8d017cf3416aa8d4a819ad32e5c549d3b8b","tid":2325401,"uid":75570,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T14:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade238e854bacb4de9fa9c45b35fc74f724e4693","tid":2325401,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T16:13:13.000Z","msg":"哈"},{"pid":"b33e41471083608c38b5b21eb361999e4d5d6c72","tid":2325401,"uid":228223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T02:35:45.000Z","msg":"人哋有大衛施華喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4276afaf1d944f935a2b295c241c0e37f0adb3","tid":2325401,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b33e41471083608c38b5b21eb361999e4d5d6c72","tid":2325401,"uid":